# GOLDEN-EMPTY Rcontra
# GROUND-TRUTH: g is one filtered jet collection; Rcontra requires size(g)>=2 AND size(g)==0 simultaneously, which no integer count can satisfy. No event passes: {}, {2 jets}, and {1 jet} all fail. The tool reports Rcontra in EMPTY REGIONS (provably selects no events).
# Contradictory size cuts on the same object make the region provably empty.

object g
  take Jet
  select pt > 30

region Rcontra
  select size(g) >= 2
  select size(g) == 0
